            <title>[LU-19176] ENOTSUPP (524) not recognized by mpifileutils</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19176</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mpifileutils complains when it gets a return value of ENOTSUPP (524) instead of ENOTSUP or EOPNOTSUPP. This is fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14301&quot; title=&quot;EOPNOTSUPP, ENOTSUPP, ENOTSUP confusion&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14301&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-14301&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, however not all of the patches are in lustre 2.15. Apply &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14301&quot; title=&quot;EOPNOTSUPP, ENOTSUPP, ENOTSUP confusion&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14301&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-14301&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; client: use EOPNOTSUPP instead of ENOTSUPP&quot; to lustre 2.15.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
